    <text x="150" y="312" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = +1.0</text>
    <text x="150" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">出来高すべてが買い圧力</text>
    <line x1="350" y1="90" x2="350" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="330" y1="170" x2="370" y2="170" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="380" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">高値</text>
    <text x="380" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">安値</text>
    <text x="350" y="288" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">終値 = 中間</text>
    <text x="350" y="312" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = 0</text>
    <text x="350" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">買い・売り圧力が半々</text>
    <line x1="550" y1="90" x2="550" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="530" y1="250" x2="570" y2="250" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="580" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">高値</text>
    <text x="580" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">安値</text>
    <text x="550" y="288" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">終値 = 安値</text>
    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = −1.0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">出来高すべてが売り圧力</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = 直近21日のMFV合計 ÷ 直近21日の出来高合計</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="ja" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ この図は資金流量乗数(MFM)の公式が終値の位置に応じてどのように値を割り当てるかを示す概念図であり、実際のローソク足データではない。</p>
  </div>
