    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = -1.0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Todo el volumen cuenta como presión vendedora</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = suma del MFV en 21 días / suma del volumen en 21 días</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="es" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ Este diagrama es una ilustración conceptual de cómo el Multiplicador de Flujo de Dinero asigna un valor según la posición del cierre — no representa datos de velas reales.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="de">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Der Money Flow Multiplier (MFM): Die Position des Schlusskurses bestimmt das Vorzeichen</text>
    <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = [(Schlusskurs−Tief) − (Hoch−Schlusskurs)] / (Hoch−Tief)</text>
    <line x1="150" y1="90" x2="150" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="130" y1="90" x2="170" y2="90" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="180" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Hoch</text>
    <text x="180" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Tief</text>
    <text x="150" y="288" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Schlusskurs = Hoch</text>
    <text x="150" y="312" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = +1,0</text>
    <text x="150" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Gesamtes Volumen als Kaufdruck gewertet</text>
    <line x1="350" y1="90" x2="350" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="330" y1="170" x2="370" y2="170" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="380" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Hoch</text>
    <text x="380" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Tief</text>
    <text x="350" y="288" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Schlusskurs = Mitte</text>
    <text x="350" y="312" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = 0</text>
    <text x="350" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Kauf- und Verkaufsdruck je zur Hälfte</text>
    <line x1="550" y1="90" x2="550" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="530" y1="250" x2="570" y2="250" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="580" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Hoch</text>
    <text x="580" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Tief</text>
    <text x="550" y="288" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Schlusskurs = Tief</text>
    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = −1,0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Gesamtes Volumen als Verkaufsdruck gewertet</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = Summe der MFV der letzten 21 Tage ÷ Summe des Volumens der letzten 21 Tage</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="de" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ Diese Grafik ist eine konzeptionelle Darstellung, wie der Money Flow Multiplier abhängig von der Position des Schlusskurses einen Wert zuweist, und bildet keine tatsächlichen Kerzendaten ab.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="fr">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Le Money Flow Multiplier (MFM) : la position de la clôture détermine le signe</text>
    <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = [(Clôture-Plus bas) - (Plus haut-Clôture)] / (Plus haut-Plus bas)</text>
    <line x1="150" y1="90" x2="150" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="130" y1="90" x2="170" y2="90" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="180" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Plus haut</text>
    <text x="180" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Plus bas</text>
    <text x="150" y="288" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Clôture = Plus haut</text>
    <text x="150" y="312" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = +1,0</text>
    <text x="150" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Tout le volume compté en pression acheteuse</text>
    <line x1="350" y1="90" x2="350" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="330" y1="170" x2="370" y2="170" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="380" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Plus haut</text>
    <text x="380" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Plus bas</text>
    <text x="350" y="288" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Clôture = Milieu</text>
    <text x="350" y="312" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = 0</text>
    <text x="350" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Réparti à parts égales, achat/vente</text>
    <line x1="550" y1="90" x2="550" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="530" y1="250" x2="570" y2="250" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="580" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Plus haut</text>
    <text x="580" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Plus bas</text>
    <text x="550" y="288" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Clôture = Plus bas</text>
    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = −1,0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Tout le volume compté en pression vendeuse</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = somme des MFV sur 21 jours / somme des volumes sur 21 jours</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="fr" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ Ce schéma illustre de façon conceptuelle comment le Money Flow Multiplier attribue une valeur selon la position de la clôture — il ne représente pas des données de chandelier réelles.</p>
</div>
  <div class="pt">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">O Money Flow Multiplier (MFM): a posição do fechamento determina o sinal</text>
    <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = [(Fechamento-Mínima) - (Máxima-Fechamento)] / (Máxima-Mínima)</text>
    <line x1="150" y1="90" x2="150" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="130" y1="90" x2="170" y2="90" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="180" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Máxima</text>
    <text x="180" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Mínima</text>
    <text x="150" y="288" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Fechamento = Máxima</text>
    <text x="150" y="312" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = +1.0</text>
    <text x="150" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Todo o volume conta como pressão compradora</text>
    <line x1="350" y1="90" x2="350" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="330" y1="170" x2="370" y2="170" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="380" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Máxima</text>
    <text x="380" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Mínima</text>
    <text x="350" y="288" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Fechamento = Ponto médio</text>
    <text x="350" y="312" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = 0</text>
    <text x="350" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Divisão igual entre compra e venda</text>
    <line x1="550" y1="90" x2="550" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="530" y1="250" x2="570" y2="250" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="580" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Máxima</text>
    <text x="580" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Mínima</text>
    <text x="550" y="288" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Fechamento = Mínima</text>
    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = -1.0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Todo o volume conta como pressão vendedora</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = soma do MFV em 21 dias / soma do volume em 21 dias</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="pt" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ Este diagrama é uma ilustração conceitual de como o Money Flow Multiplier atribui um valor com base na posição do fechamento — ele não representa dados reais de candles.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="tr">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Para Akışı Çarpanı (MFM): Kapanış Konumu İşareti Belirler</text>
    <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = [(Kapanış−Düşük) − (Yüksek−Kapanış)] / (Yüksek−Düşük)</text>
    <line x1="150" y1="90" x2="150" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="130" y1="90" x2="170" y2="90" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="180" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Yüksek</text>
    <text x="180" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Düşük</text>
    <text x="150" y="288" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Kapanış = Yüksek</text>
    <text x="150" y="312" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = +1.0</text>
    <text x="150" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Hacmin tamamı alım baskısı sayılır</text>
    <line x1="350" y1="90" x2="350" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="330" y1="170" x2="370" y2="170" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="380" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Yüksek</text>
    <text x="380" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Düşük</text>
    <text x="350" y="288" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Kapanış = Orta Nokta</text>
    <text x="350" y="312" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = 0</text>
    <text x="350" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Alım ve satım baskısı eşit paylaşılır</text>
    <line x1="550" y1="90" x2="550" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="530" y1="250" x2="570" y2="250" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="580" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Yüksek</text>
    <text x="580" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Düşük</text>
    <text x="550" y="288" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Kapanış = Düşük</text>
    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = −1.0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Hacmin tamamı satış baskısı sayılır</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = son 21 günün MFV toplamı ÷ son 21 günün hacim toplamı</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="tr" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ Bu diyagram, Para Akışı Çarpanı (MFM) formülünün kapanış konumuna göre nasıl bir değer atadığını gösteren kavramsal bir şemadır ve gerçek mum verisi değildir.</p>
</div>
  <div class="vi">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Hệ số dòng tiền (MFM): Vị trí giá đóng cửa quyết định dấu</text>
    <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = [(Đóng cửa-Thấp nhất) - (Cao nhất-Đóng cửa)] / (Cao nhất-Thấp nhất)</text>
    <line x1="150" y1="90" x2="150" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="130" y1="90" x2="170" y2="90" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="180" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Cao nhất</text>
    <text x="180" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Thấp nhất</text>
    <text x="150" y="288" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Đóng cửa = Cao nhất</text>
    <text x="150" y="312" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = +1.0</text>
    <text x="150" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Toàn bộ khối lượng là áp lực mua</text>
    <line x1="350" y1="90" x2="350" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="330" y1="170" x2="370" y2="170" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="380" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Cao nhất</text>
    <text x="380" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Thấp nhất</text>
    <text x="350" y="288" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Đóng cửa = Trung điểm</text>
    <text x="350" y="312" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = 0</text>
    <text x="350" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Áp lực mua và bán chia đều</text>
    <line x1="550" y1="90" x2="550" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="530" y1="250" x2="570" y2="250" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="580" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Cao nhất</text>
    <text x="580" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Thấp nhất</text>
    <text x="550" y="288" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Đóng cửa = Thấp nhất</text>
    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = -1.0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Toàn bộ khối lượng là áp lực bán</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = tổng MFV 21 ngày / tổng khối lượng 21 ngày</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="vi" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ Biểu đồ này minh họa khái niệm về cách công thức Hệ số dòng tiền (MFM) gán giá trị dựa trên vị trí giá đóng cửa, và không phải là dữ liệu nến thực tế.</p>
</div>
<div class="ru">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">The Money Flow Multiplier (MFM): Close Position Determines the Sign</text>
    <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = [(Close-Low) - (High-Close)] / (High-Low)</text>
    <line x1="150" y1="90" x2="150" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="130" y1="90" x2="170" y2="90" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="180" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">High</text>
    <text x="180" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Low</text>
    <text x="150" y="288" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Close = High</text>
    <text x="150" y="312" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = +1.0</text>
    <text x="150" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">All volume counted as buying</text>
    <line x1="350" y1="90" x2="350" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="330" y1="170" x2="370" y2="170" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="380" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">High</text>
    <text x="380" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Low</text>
    <text x="350" y="288" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Close = Midpoint</text>
    <text x="350" y="312" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = 0</text>
    <text x="350" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Split evenly, buy vs sell</text>
    <line x1="550" y1="90" x2="550" y2="250" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="530" y1="250" x2="570" y2="250" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="6"/>
    <text x="580" y="94" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">High</text>
    <text x="580" y="254" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Low</text>
    <text x="550" y="288" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Close = Low</text>
    <text x="550" y="312" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">MFM = -1.0</text>
    <text x="550" y="336" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">All volume counted as selling</text>
    <text x="350" y="380" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">CMF = sum of MFV over 21 days / sum of volume over 21 days</text>
  </svg>
